name: YOKO WANTS TO KNOW WHATS FOR DINNER
description:
We made a little paper tie for Yokovich and he loved it. Understanding more optical flow and frame blending. Part of our San Isidros experiments. 1920 X 1080px dusty animated GIF, 64 colors. 

EXPERIMENTATION WITH CATS, GOOD. 

EXPERIMENTATION WITH HUMANS, BAD.
